\c 41 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 41\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Kadhata Nama Dhukkubsatee Fira Dhabee (Geggeessituu warra faarfattootaaf; faarfannaa Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Namni isa dadhabaadhaaf yaadu haa gammadu! Waaqayyo guyyaa hamaatti isa in oolcha.
\m \bd 2\bd* Waaqayyo isa in eega, jireenyas in kennaaf; biyya keessattis "Isa gammade" in jedhama, yaa gooftaa ati, gojomii diinota isaatti dabarsitee isa hin kennitu.
\m \bd 3\bd* Waaqayyo siree dhukkubaa irratti ol isa in qaba, fayyisees siree dhukkubaa irraa isa in kaasa.
\m \bd 4\bd* Ani immoo, "Yaa Waaqayyo, anaaf oo'i, ani si duratti cubbuu hojjedheera, na fayyisi!" jedhee kadhadheera.
\m \bd 5\bd* Diinonni koo hamaa ana irratti in dubbatu, "Inni yoom du'a, maqaan isaas yoom lafa irraa bada?" in jedhu.
\m \bd 6\bd* Namni ana ilaaluu dhufu, sobee anaa wajjin in haasa'a, garaa isaatti immoo dubbii hamaa kuufatee karaatti ba'ee isa in odeessa;
\m \bd 7\bd* warri ana jibban hundinuu waa'ee koo walitti in hasaasu, wanta hamaa yaadanii ana irratti in qopheessu.
\m \bd 8\bd* Isaan, "Dubbii gadheetu isa irra ga'e, lafa ciisees deebi'ee hin ka'u" in jedhu.
\m \bd 9\bd* Namni garaa kootii, inni ani amanadhe, inni buddeena koo nyaate illee ana dhiituuf miilla ol fudhate.
\m \bd 10\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, ati faara anaaf toli, diinota kootiif dugda akkan baasutti lafan ciisee ana kaasi.
\m \bd 11\bd* Yeroo diinonni koo sagalee mo'ichaa ana irratti dhageessisuu dadhaban, anatti gammaduu kee ani kanaan nan beeka.
\m \bd 12\bd* Ani balleessaa malee waanan argamuuf, ati ol qajeelchitee na qabda, bara baraanis of dura na dhaabda.
\m \bd 13\bd* Waaqayyo gooftaan Israa'el, maqaan isaa baraa hamma bara baraatti haa eebbifamu! Ameen! Ameen!
\b 
